The spacious and well-appointed bedrooms feature ample closet space and large windows that allow for plenty of natural light. The master bedroom boasts a luxurious en-suite bathroom while the other two bedrooms share two additional full bathrooms.

The ground floor of this townhouse features a welcoming living room that provides the perfect space for relaxation and entertainment. The living room opens up to a spacious backyard that is perfect for hosting barbeques, outdoor activities, or simply enjoying the beautiful Dubai weather.

Residents of this charming townhouse can enjoy the convenience of being within walking distance of the community pool, where they can cool off and soak up the sun on hot days. This is a brand-new townhouse development by Emaar Properties Sun Townhouses. The development features exclusively designed 3 and 4-bedroom units in the prime location of Arabian Ranches III – (JOY), Dubai. The townhouses have a modern interior design and high-end finishing.

The 3-bedroom townhouse has a built-up area of 1943.20 sq. ft. and comes with a maid's room. The townhouse faces amenities, providing easy access to the children's play room, park and swimming pool. The property is ready to move in and comes with a 1-year warranty.

Joy Townhouses are located in the premier neighborhood of Arabian Ranches III, which provides numerous outdoor facilities from the other clusters, including a lazy river, splash deck, and sports activities. The development is located in a lush green landscape, providing residents with a serene and comfortable environment.

Residents of Sun Townhouses can easily access the city through interconnected road networks to Sheikh Mohammed Bin Zayed Road and the Dubai Global Village. The development also offers a direct connection to the 86 Km long Al Qudra Cycling Track.
